node.text: A before and after… same barber just 3 years apart. This picture doesnt even show how bad it truly was…Acne was a huge struggle of mine, the endless days and nights wondering when I’ll like the way I look, waking up every morning walking into the bathroom and not being able to look at my self because I felt hideous, having no confidence to leave the house and when I did I made sure I had a mask with me. I know there’s a lot of people who struggle with acne, I know how hard it is. Others may never know the struggle or feeling of having acne. For the people that do, it gets better I promise and there are plenty of solutions that work such as accutane, it was the holy grail for me. Be patient and truly find love in your self while you feel down about your self because when you get through it you’ll learn to love and appreciate your self more.
